# For React applications specifically for deployment
# If you are using create-react-app, `build` folder is ignored by default.
# For GitHub Pages, the `build` folder needs to be pushed if you serve from root.
# If you are deploying to GitHub Pages by pushing the `build` folder to a `gh-pages` branch,
# you might need to adjust your build and deploy scripts.
# Usually, for `user.github.io` repos, the `main` branch is served, so `build` content goes there.